                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">For my capstone project I for my UX Design bootcamp at Springboard, I chose a new business idea for a crowdfunding birthday gifting app. The initial concept for the idea features a self-hosted birthday wish. </p>
                <br>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">I knew that people are willing to contribute to a crowdfunded gift, but I was not sure if they'd contribute to a campaign that someone ran for their own benefit. So let's go build an app.... oh wait, first let's conduct some research.</p>
