<section class="">
    <div class="">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="column">
                <h1 class="title has-text-centered is-spaced is-size-1-desktop is-size-2-tablet is-size3-mobile has-text-grey-darker">RESEARCH FINDINGS</h1>
                <h3 class="subtitle has-text-centered has-text-grey-darker">Individuals are not willing to donate to an individual that wants a gift for themselves.</h3>
                <br>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">I ran a brief survey that helped me to narrow down who to interview. I qualified a handful of individuals that fit a range of novice to pro users of crowdfunding platforms such as Kickstarter.</p>
                <br>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">I then interviewed 4 individuals for my initial research to validate whether or not people will donate to a campaign that is promoted by an individual indicating what birthday gift they'd like to receive.</p>
                <br>
                <h3 class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">Main Highlights:</h3>
                <ul class="">
                    <li class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left">• People are not willing to donate to a self promoting campaign, but are for a group-led campaign.</li>
                    <li class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left">• People are willing to donate to a campaign that gives a gift without getting anything in return.</li>
                    <li class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left">• They would be willing to spend about $20 towards a gift for a friend.</li>
                    <li class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left">• Individuals would be willing to donate about twice as much if a portion goes to a charity.</li>
                    <li class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left">• They expect that between 20-50% will go to a charity.</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">See Research Summary <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_2veuBsRJdzYsG56yVmZYUfERc8IPWwvGQXuldIV5qQ/edit">here</a>.</p>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker">Empathy Map <a href="https://docs.google.com/drawings/d/1IQwsX9SpGujpJpyZtIvgb-DVjf0ZKnKOZNrVQoaaOw8/edit" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
                <p class="subtitle is-6 is-narrow-left has-text-grey-darker"></p>
